---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Parry"
  description="Parry's privacy policy. Learn how we handle your data, what we collect, and how your messages are processed."
  canonicalPath="/privacy"
>
  <section class="px-5 py-16 md:px-8 md:py-20">
    <div class="prose-legal mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="mb-2 font-[var(--font-sora)] text-3xl font-bold md:text-4xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mb-8 text-sm text-text-tertiary">Last updated: February 2026</p>

      <h2>Introduction</h2>
      <p>
        Parry ("we", "our", "us") operates the Parry mobile application. This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when you use our app.
      </p>

      <h2>Information Collection and Use</h2>

      <h3>Data We Collect</h3>
      <p><strong>Usage Data:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Anonymous user identifier (for subscription management)</li>
        <li>App usage analytics (screens viewed, features used)</li>
        <li>Crash reports and error logs</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>Message Content:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Messages you input are sent to Anthropic (our AI provider) for processing via their Claude API</li>
        <li>We do <strong>NOT</strong> store your message content on our servers</li>
        <li>Anthropic may retain message data for up to 30 days for safety monitoring purposes</li>
        <li>Your message data is <strong>NOT</strong> used to train AI models</li>
        <li>After the 30-day safety window, message data is deleted by Anthropic</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>Data We Do NOT Collect:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your name or email (unless you contact support)</li>
        <li>Your phone number</li>
        <li>Your contacts</li>
        <li>Your location</li>
        <li>Your messages outside of what you explicitly input</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>How We Use Your Data</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>To provide AI-generated response suggestions</li>
        <li>To manage your subscription</li>
        <li>To improve our app through anonymous analytics</li>
        <li>To fix bugs and improve performance</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use the following services that may collect data:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Anthropic (Claude AI)</strong> — Processes your message input to generate responses. <a href="https://www.anthropic.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Privacy Policy</a></li>
        <li><strong>Supabase</strong> — Stores anonymous user preferences. <a href="https://supabase.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Privacy Policy</a></li>
        <li><strong>RevenueCat</strong> — Manages subscriptions and purchases. <a href="https://www.revenuecat.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Privacy Policy</a></li>
        <li><strong>Sentry</strong> — Error tracking and crash reporting. <a href="https://sentry.io/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Privacy Policy</a></li>
        <li><strong>PostHog</strong> — Product analytics. <a href="https://posthog.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Privacy Policy</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Data Retention</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Anonymous user data:</strong> Retained while you use the app</li>
        <li><strong>AI processing data:</strong> Retained by Anthropic for up to 30 days for safety monitoring; not used for model training</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics data:</strong> Aggregated and anonymized</li>
        <li><strong>Crash reports:</strong> Retained for 90 days</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You can:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Request deletion of your data by contacting us</li>
        <li>Opt out of analytics by uninstalling the app</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        Our app is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children under 13.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us:<br />
        Email: <a href="mailto:support@parryai.app">support@parryai.app</a>
      </p>

      <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-text-tertiary">&copy; 2026 Parry. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
